<div class = ""card-panel hoverable""><p class=AAE-Normal dir=LTR>On this window, enter the last three digits of the
serial number of the device in the fourth part of the IP field. To connect to
the device, click on “CONNECT”. If a new version is connected to the device,
the &quot;Firmware&quot; of the device will be updated once and after the green
bar is filled, the device will be connected in a few seconds. To connect via
Wi-Fi, the switch on the back of the device needs to be set on “Wi-Fi”. Then,
from the &quot;Wi-Fi&quot; in quick launch bar on the laptop, find and select
the Wi-Fi connection of the device. The password for this connection is the
serial number available from the label attached to the side of the device. Once
the connection is complete, click on “Setting” on the start page of the
software. On this page, enter the last two digits of the serial number of the
deivce in th");
